{"tid":406760,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"公務員係咪唔買醫療保險都得？","createTime":"2017-09-20T02:17:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T16:43:29.000Z","uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2f2fed7486920c39446fec7cb486fb497f6175ca","tid":406760,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T02:17:03.000Z","msg":"有無for 公務員既plan?"},{"pid":"83688b80a6686e81ac93e588457e54d91565fe09","tid":406760,"uid":20602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T02:19:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無for 公務員既plan?</blockquote><br />\n咪有CIRCULAR 出左有幾間公司出左自願醫保可以買。<br />\n<br />\n公務員係睇政府醫生唔洗錢，你要睇私家醫生一樣要比錢。所以睇下你自己覺得需要有幾大"},{"pid":"8ab88176ae483359b3a054b765c291bc138381a2","tid":406760,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T15:50:46.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"eb1782d6926665d137c5591ae9d6fe98f0e17177","tid":406760,"uid":23786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T15:54:59.000Z","msg":"靠政府，排睇牙排到二零一九<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81de55b263e260b92a53a2ddf58b0f387d80e648","tid":406760,"uid":128563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:16:56.000Z","msg":"公務員睇公立醫院唔洗錢，不過如果有啲病想同相熟嘅私家醫生做，或者想住私家醫院環境好啲嘅。咁就建議有返一份個人醫療保險。<br />\n有咩問題可以聯絡：<a href=\"https://t.me/kurokinonenon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fkurokinonenon&d=JFlsvJM%2Ft%2FzLb4bQ1ssAGr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=73de4fc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/kurokinonenon</a>"},{"pid":"a2b15f862501bc9680b82636de833547c87e7a21","tid":406760,"uid":146039,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:34:41.000Z","msg":"巴打，如果覺得公務員嘅保障唔夠，就要買多份醫保保障自己。小弟做間公司都有醫療福利，但係得8萬保障，入一入私院check 一 check 都分分鐘唔夠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  最近遇到個好嘅agent,  話我知原來我可以買份醫保入私院check,  如果check 到有咩cancer，可以揾醫生轉介返去公立，返到公立即刻醫唔洗再慢慢排隊，仲可以慳返一大筆保險費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好agent 可遇不可求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你可以WhatsApp 我分享下經驗俾你聽， 我電話59830266"},{"pid":"ab0910a52da8116075a2ac32e6aebbb1d23cfe4f","tid":406760,"uid":24909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T15:00:10.000Z","msg":"去公立醫院畀班姑娘粗聲粗氣<br />\n啲覆診個期又耐 問多兩句都唔濕你<br />\n利申 身份證M字 澳門人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feee8ea0f134f96ba645bac3f5ae4a15ee745f1e","tid":406760,"uid":55327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T16:43:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}